Invocation Name: my calorie count
des:
Skill which can help user to know total calorific value associated with a food item. So, that you can monitor your daily calorie intake and then take necessary measures according to it.
Currently Indian dishes like Capati, Tomato Chicken, Vegetable Biryani, etc are supported.

Complete list of supported items : https://gist.github.com/Nitish18/99e8ede243777820e190b4810d391a9f
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
